e":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee53fa6ccf892cb6633f6086f1cf0081d860bb77","tid":1652544,"uid":181362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有post話獅鳥果陣可以係旁邊嗌點解要叫佢 等live片出街果陣有利我地<br />\n「打手足呀啦！」<br />\n「你郁手先架！我自衛咋！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"Yup. 助氣詞全部叫晒藍屍罪行. 大大聲叫. 要直播聽到晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d62adb12084b0d8990d5733b2c7c4c7d1264e8","tid":1652544,"uid":277363,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"返商場Part time日撚日比人屌<br />\n最撚煩就係啲啊公啊婆<br />\n死唔撚斷氣咁鬧鳩你<br />\n而你係完全唔明佢嗡乜鳩<br />\n同後生中年既都可以講解釋下<br />\n同佢地跟本講唔撚通。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係connect 啊公啊婆走去屌狗<br />\n真係無撚敵，唔係講笑<br />\n還嘴你又唔知講乜好，又唔可以郁手<br />\n唔好講郁手，你班狗實玩撚完<br />\n淨係反屌幾句大聲比人影到<br />\n啲狗乜道德高地都冇哂。"},{"pid":"422d13ae55baf934e9fa7e53dede213045a502ea","tid":1652544,"uid":271248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"7c550bd25cb18d7fc21b2cbeed15701cbeb913a0","tid":1652544,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eae5060b9cb3964051c2cee94931ab5b6b42ada8","tid":1652544,"uid":238424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"[觀塘撚必入]不分化指責=/=不檢討、要士氣=/=打飛機，唔該快撚啲認清我地係打緊仗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652537</a>"},{"pid":"ffcb62608f24a016d8cf56f44befea4c5b31d3d0","tid":1652544,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:33:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a31b5de98f14014993d3b60e30857f1e32d5045d","tid":1652544,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"