ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"baa141cbf59e7a8292dde824bf14cbbc668395bc","tid":1652544,"uid":297996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:51:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cb07d926a9805b9b82e087f749c98134e8d3107","tid":1652544,"uid":135124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"之前有手足試過好似拳擊賽咁舉牌 上面寫住「藍絲打人」大家可以仿效下 同埋一路鶳個陣可以一路講「打人吖嗱！」"},{"pid":"ae1673ed918313a2c128ca0f874e1eef67f1f713","tid":1652544,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"睇龍珠話: 神獸出現時，周邊既人一定要大聲許願，好靈既！"},{"pid":"7b3f612e5bb65a537daf3e549a1cc93e51caffd8","tid":1652544,"uid":219146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb4feed100382310678c19feca7f87f517a617a3","tid":1652544,"uid":279928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"話說 今日又有個阿婆走埋嚟又拍我膊頭<br />\n<br />\n阿婆=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「今日又見到幾個叔叔姨姨俾人打到流晒血. 冇眼睇lor.. 平時我都係支持班後生仔. 但係今日飲茶俾隔離邨阿陳伯問到我口啞啞. 可唔可以再話我知點解佢哋咁樣做」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  「佢哋全部都係先郁手打人. 仲有刀係身. 依家報警靠班黑警冇用. 隨時原告變被告. <br />\n <br />\n好似屯門個白衫阿伯咁. 揸刀追住後生仔想斬人再先. 後生仔已經好克制咁自衛. 之後阿伯就自己冚親個頭流晒血咁<br />\n<br />\n再好似之前個紅色的士佬咁. 揸車係人群入面加速撞上行人路. 撞斷左個女仔對腳. 骨都斷晒. 之後阿伯就自己跌落車又仆親個頭流晒血咁. 警察最後竟然控告返俾人撞嘅路人甲. 的士佬撞人居然可以冇罪. 仲有360嗰老闆，即係之前嗰班揸刀白衫佬咧，捐左52萬俾佢做棺材本. 婆婆你話報警仲有冇用啦. 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  「哎呀. 衰仔. 呢啲嘢要大聲講出嚟呀嘛. 你地貼係蓮儂牆俾阿婆我用放大鏡睇下都好呀嘛. 你咁樣同啲電視台一樣. 只係播班老坑冚親個頭啲畫面. 又唔講點解. 算啦. 算啦. 唔好阻住我搵隔離邨阿陳伯報仇」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「........」<br />\n<br />\n我覺得阿婆今次又講得好啱. 好多大年紀嘅人都唔識上網上連登. 又成日睇埋cctvb啲狗屎垃圾新聞.得個報導時間係真. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左更加多中立/淺藍 轉態.</strong></span> 我地文宣應該開始做嘢.<br />\n<br />\n1. 前線手足自衛完可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>直接將藍屍嘅罪行寫係張紙到貼係佢身上or附近地下.</strong></span> 最好中英文對照. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>確保記者們都可以影到藍屍嘅同時影埋罪行.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 連儂牆上面都可以貼下各位冚親頭跌跛腳藍屍嘅所作所為. 俾更加多人知道. 手足只係出於自衛. 因為黑警已經唔可以相信.<br />\n<br />\n可以參考鋪頭裝修嘅做法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1649087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1649087</a><br />\n<br />\n希望可以Connect到更加多嘅公公婆婆. 又俾國際知道班藍屍嘅所作所為.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>千奇唔好睇少阿公阿婆嘅威力. 屌起popo上嚟. 勇武都驚.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家有更好嘅idea都可以留言分享.<br />\n<br />\n最後.<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>宇宙大爆炸都唔割蓆!</strong></span><br />\n🇭🇰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！<br />\n缺一不可！</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"人人帶marker同紙<br />\n就算冇紙都唔緊要<br />\n寫落佢件衫度"},{"pid":"4d2d30bc7637cc1b12667f3e57b0afcaa9c9b5b8","tid":1652544,"uid":228326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"9f55a8f1a80f6ae6c8545888e27ef11f3409e0ea","tid":1652544,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a721377e2003e5b835bb3de930c97de83cce8e","tid":1652544,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"Tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cb22b86cf46fded14f695606e68a27e9c6cd33","tid":1652544,"uid":113327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"a2c97272b091d51f49368f793c2d475559959ad0","tid":1652544,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"連儂場貼吓該區仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住大大隻字要話畀大家知佢衰乜<br />\n<br />\n阿婆啟發咗大家"},{"pid":"007586bc6d88616b3621daa1314ddeb02bc2da91","tid":1652544,"uid":322836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"啱啊<br />\n我嫲嫲都70幾歲，唔識上網，都淨係睇tvb<br />\n有時提翻我出面危險，講tvb播嘅嘢我聽<br />\n但我會話翻佢知真正事實係點<br />\n起碼佢知咩事先，答翻我原來係咁㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜佢嗰邊少資訊<br />\n兩位老人家住深藍油塘<br />\n等見面先可以講咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a964974c1665b9f940893634df057f552ae0975a","tid":1652544,"uid":302758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"我諗到制裁國難五金既辦法！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d522bf029901e19ceb4b2cb3ea09824e2714b9e","tid":1652544,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:56:35.000Z","msg":"推推推 連儂需要更多長輩圖"},{"pid":"3958526aa0e15f6421801a70d4d7b096ceca4da9","tid":1652544,"uid":261072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"091154afa986d9600432a9095cd56d22072abc7b","tid":1652544,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"最好字大圖大 鮮紅色"},{"pid":"8b895bb4741a80abdec8b6fda3600f35401e9083","tid":1652544,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:56:54.000Z","msg":"文宣落力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0d653393ed7a9a8f6dd92a1e559272f4dd4aaa","tid":1652544,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76a26ca141f3144bfd5bef4bcab45508def991f","tid":1652544,"uid":102010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"657d418ae72eb2fafe326bc3a820b05039128da2","tid":1652544,"uid":102010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0