 />\n而你係完全唔明佢嗡乜鳩<br />\n同後生中年既都可以講解釋下<br />\n同佢地跟本講唔撚通。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係connect 啊公啊婆走去屌狗<br />\n真係無撚敵，唔係講笑<br />\n還嘴你又唔知講乜好，又唔可以郁手<br />\n唔好講郁手，你班狗實玩撚完<br />\n淨係反屌幾句大聲比人影到<br />\n啲狗乜道德高地都冇哂。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:44:47.000Z","msg":"2個鐘後重新睇你句「唔可以郁手」好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有銀髮被班犬暴力拉咗"},{"pid":"f5b72ed9adae85d7d855d6a251b20fbb4c08f354","tid":1652544,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee53fa6ccf892cb6633f6086f1cf0081d860bb77","tid":1652544,"uid":181362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有post話獅鳥果陣可以係旁邊嗌點解要叫佢 等live片出街果陣有利我地<br />\n「打手足呀啦！」<br />\n「你郁手先架！我自衛咋！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4846e1da443f82ef26e5d5881c2a921cafe5119","tid":1652544,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:08:07.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"e79ef50c56701fd9246dc5c66a7ef4b77a517258","tid":1652544,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"0167e181420a98740dea0c054898d210fc69138f","tid":1652544,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93f8f0f300240553e1d719dde203616575793cbf","tid":1652544,"uid":252620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:16:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa13bc655b1581cd473ab7e2ff7f150bade826af","tid":1652544,"uid":57767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo